LOCUS       pEGB2Ω2_SF-35s:hCas9:tNos_(GB1103) 12511 bp    DNA     circular SYN 15-DEC-2025
DEFINITION  Transcriptional unit for (human codon optimized) Cas9 plant
            expression driven by the 35S promoter. Specially conceived to be
            linked with the TU of the kanamycin resistance gene GB1181..
